		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p>At his thirtieth high-school reunion, <strong><span class="smallcaps">Sparrow</span></strong> danced to &ldquo;Play That Funky Music, White Boy&rdquo; with a criminal lawyer. He describes his latest book, <em>Yes, You ARE a Revolutionary: Plus 7 Other Books</em> (Soft Skull Press), as &ldquo;a compilation of my greatest hits, as I define them.&rdquo; He lives in Phoenicia, New York, where he anxiously awaits the <span class="smallcaps">NEA</span>&rsquo;s response to his grant proposal.</p><a href="/contributors/sparrow" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
